    "notes": "Compact schema-linking SFT run. This keeps the Exp033 schema-linking hypothesis but caps notes to two tables and six columns so the local RTX 2080 Ti can produce a feasibility signal. Train rows use gold-SQL-derived schema_linking_notes as supervised metadata. Eval rows use question/schema/value-note-derived schema_linking_notes only, never gold SQL. This is a local one-shot SFT experiment, not an official benchmark score."
